@startuml
actor Student
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Django Server" as Server
participant "Database" as DB

Student -> Browser: Open Assignment Submission Page
Browser -> Server: Request assignment form
Server -> DB: Fetch assignment details
DB --> Server: Return details
Server --> Browser: Display form

Student -> Browser: Upload file and submit
Browser -> Server: Send submission data
Server -> DB: Save submission record
DB --> Server: Confirmation
Server --> Browser: Display success message
@enduml

